{
  "texts": [
    "Besides, it supports the concern for responsible and ethical use of AI in security, without which people cannot be assured of trusting their security and wellbeing in the hands of the subsequently automated security systems.",
    "The encryption methods utilized by intrusion detection systems stand to benefit greatly from the implementation of Quantum Key Distribution (QKD).",
    "The mathematical algorithms used in conventional encryption systems are theoretically vulnerable to powerful computers.",
    "In contrast, QKD employs quantum mechanical principles to ensure the absolute safety of data transmission 48.",
    "It allows two people generate a secret key that can't be hacked or intercepted by anyone, regardless of how powerful their computers are."
  ]
}